      <div xml:id="NA382-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu oruvaḻit taṇanta kālattup poḻutu paṭa āṟṟāḷāki niṉṟa talaimakaḷait tōḻi āṟṟuvikkallāḷ āyiṉāṭkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what SHE said to the confidante who was encouraging HER who stood there as one who was unable to bear it when time passed in the time when [HE] had departed on a temporary absence.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA382">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          kāṉaṉ mālaik kaḻinīr malka</l>
<l>          nīṉiṟa neyta ṉiraiyitaḻ porunta</l>
<l>          vāṉā talaikkuṅ kaṭaṉmī ṉaruntip</l>
<l>          puḷḷiṉaṅ kuṭampai yuṭaṉcēr puḷḷār</l>
<l>          tuṟantōr tēet tiruntunaṉi varunti</l>
<l>          yāruyi raḻiva tāyiṉu nēriḻai</l>
<l>          karattal vēṇṭumāṉ maṟṟē parappunīrt</l>
<l>          taṇṇan tuṟaiva ṉāṇa</l>
<l>          naṇṇār tūṟṟum paḻitā ṉuṇṭē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          Even if [our] difficult lives go to ruin, [you of] fine jewels,</l>
<l rend="indent3">          suffering much upon being in the land of the one who abandoned [us],</l>
<l rend="indent">          where the birds joining together in the nest with flocks of birds become full</l>
<l rend="indent3">          eating fish from the sea that dashes unendingly,</l>
<l rend="indent2">          while the water increases in the backwaters at evening in the forest,</l>
<l rend="indent2">          while the petals fold themselves in rows on the blue-coloured waterlilies,</l>
<l>        – it is just necessary indeed to hide [this].</l>
<l>        Blame itself it is which the foes are spreading,</l>
<l rend="indent">          for the man from the cool ghat of extensive waters to be ashamed.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
